description: Screenshots: http://www.imagesum.com/2018/11/image-1_99.html IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2249007/ Resolution: 1280x720 Format: .mp4 Audio: AAC English First episode date: June 30, 2013 Network: Showtime Awards: Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Drama Series, MORE Nominations: Writers Guild of America Award for Television: New Series, MORE Ray Donovan is a "fixer" for Hollywood's elite. He is the go-to guy that the city's celebrities, athletes and business moguls call to make their problems disappear. It's a much more lucrative job than his previous work as a ruthless South Boston thug, vaulting him within reach of the truly wealthy and powerful. But no amount of money or the expensive things it can buy can completely mask Ray's past, a past that continues to haunt him with troubled brothers always calling and his father's recent release from 20 years spent in prison. Now a free man, Ray's father, Mickey, arrives in Los Angeles to get what he feels is rightfully his. Mickey's desire to reconnect and settle old scores with his family -- including Ray's wife and kids, who have never met the family's patriarch and are anxious to get to know him -- threatens to destroy everything Ray has built for himself
